ca.mcgill.ecse321.TreePLE.service

Class ReportService

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse321.TreePLE.service.ReportService

  • @Service
public class ReportService
extends java.lang.Object
    This service class contains all the main functionalities related to generating a Sustainability Report.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      ReportService(VersionManager vm)
      The ReportService constructor verifies which version has been selected by the user, finds the TreeManager associated to that version and sets the class's TreeManager as that one for users to edit attributes on that TreeManager.
